#X text 48 603 WHEN LAUNCHED \, IF RECORD-Q ON (ONLY MANUALLY):::: \; 1- INCOMING TRIGGER BANGS ARE "LISTENED" TO \; 2- ABSOLUTE BAR TIMER WILL START \; 3- FOR EACH INCOMING TRIGGER BANG \, TIME INFORMATION WILL BE INSERTED TO THE END OF \$0-sequence \; 4- WHEN BAR DURATION IS FINISHED WITHOUT IF NO RE-LAUNCH \, STOPS LISTENING \;, f 51;
